data.description: Here's your chance to live on the golf course in Fairfield Bay, Arkansas. This 3BR/2BA home has a spacious garage, including a safe room, and sits on an oversized lot with beautiful trees on the Mountain Ranch 8th tee box. This spacious home has been updated with high-end kitchen appliances and newly enlarged master bathroom. This home sits on a quiet culdesac where you can enjoy all the great amenities of Fairfield Bay Arkansas that's been voted the safest city in Arkansas more than once. Please take a look at this before it's too late.
